    All Implemented Interfaces:
    AcceptFilter<T>, BaseFilter<T>, BaseSQLFilter<T>, BinaryFilter<T>, JoinFilter<T>, OrderFilter<T>, PatternFilter<T>, Targetted<T>
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    IndexedLinkManager.LinkFilter, TupleFactory.TupleAndFilter

    public class AndFilter<T>
extends BaseCombineFilter<T>
implements PatternFilter<T>, AcceptFilter<T>
    Combining filter that selects the intersection of multiple filters. This is a PatternFilter, BinaryFilter and an AcceptFilter though it has its own target method in FilterVisitor. It can combine AcceptFilter, BinaryFilter and PatternFilter.
    Author:
    spb
